    "For the physicochemical descriptors, HBA, AROM, and ROTB showed high importance in the order.",
    "The feature importance in the LR model was analyzed in two ways.",
    "ROTB, AROM, HBA, and substructural features of 80 and 392 were found to be of common importance in both methods.In all models, the importance of each feature was identified.",
    "Analyzing the results of the feature importance, substructural features of 80 and 464 showed a high correlation with the DILI prediction.",
